name: tumblr - Christmas Icon Bar
description: NOTE: As of 01.01.2013 this style will no longer be supported. Replaces your default tumblr Icon Bar with a Christmas icon set. Icons "jump" when hovered.
css: @namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);@-moz-document url-prefix('http://www.tumblr.com'), url-prefix('https://www.tumblr.com')  {#new_post a[class="new_post_label"] span{background-repeat:no-repeat!important;background-size:68px!important;margin-left:2px!important;padding-top:10px!important;background-position:0,0!important;top:-5px!important}#new_post a[class="new_post_label"]{padding-top:78px!important;height:4px!important}#new_post a[class="new_post_label"],#new_post a[class="new_post_label"] span{opacity:.9!important;color:rgba(0,0,0,.65)!important}#new_post a[class="new_post_label"]:hover,#new_post a[class="new_post_label"] span:hover{opacity:1!important;color:rgba(0,0,0,1)!important}#new_post a[class="new_post_label"]:hover{top:0!important}#new_post a[class="new_post_label"] span:hover{top:-10px!important}#new_post_label_text .new_post_label_icon{background:url("data:image/png;base64,")!important}#new_post_label_photo .new_post_label_icon{background:url("data:image/png;base64,")!important}#new_post_label_quote .new_post_label_icon{background:url("data:image/png;base64,")!important}#new_post_label_link .new_post_label_icon{background:url("data:image/png;base64,")!important}#new_post_label_chat .new_post_label_icon{background:url("data:image/png;base64,")!important}#new_post_label_audio .new_post_label_icon{background:url("data:image/png;base64,")!important}#new_post_label_video .new_post_label_icon{background:url("data:image/png;base64,")!important}}
